-- David Wilson and Jake Little

INSTRUCTION FORMAT
  00000000 00000000
  AAAAAAAA AAAABBBB

  A bits => instruction opcode
  B bits => addressing mode

ADDRESSING MODES
  0x0: REG, INT
  0x1: REG, REG
  0x2: REG, [REG]
  0x3: REG, [REG + INT]
  0x4: REG, [REG + REG*INT]
  0x5: [REG], REG
  0x6: [REG + INT], REG
  0x7: [REG + REG*INT], INT
